<h1>Forms</h1>

<p class="intro">
    Use form elements to obtain user input.
    They should include text that describes the action they perform.
</p>

<ol>
    <li><a href="#anchor1">Text Input</a></li>
    <li><a href="#anchor2">Text Area</a></li>
    <li><a href="#anchor3">Dropdown</a></li>
    <li><a href="#anchor4">Radio Buttons</a></li>
    <li><a href="#anchor5">Checkbox</a></li>
</ol>

<p></p>

