<h3 id="anchor2">2. Text Area</h3>

<p>Use a text area when the user is expected to enter in a larger amount of text.</p>

<h6>Standard textarea</h6>
<div class="tab-set">
    <%- partial('../../_partials/tabs', { id: 'textarea-input' }) %>
    <%- partial('../../_partials/textarea', { id: 'text-area-component' }) %>
</div>

<h3 id="anchor3">3. Dropdown</h3>

<p>Use dropdowns to contain large numbers of options or when space is at a premium.</p>

<div class="tab-set">
    <%- partial('../../_partials/tabs', { id: 'select-input' }) %>
    <%- partial('../../_partials/select', { id: 'select-dropdown' }) %>
